DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261201
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270501
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY
SUMMARY:🍄 Hedgehog Mushroom Season
DESCRIPTION:Scientific name: Hydnum repandum\nDifficulty: Easy\nHabitat: Mi
 xed forest under oak\, pine\, and fir\nSeason: Jan\, Feb\, Mar\, Apr\, Dec
 \nPeak: May\, Nov\nRegions: Marin\, East\, Peninsula\, Santacruz\n\nCream 
 to pale orange cap with tiny downward-pointing teeth instead of gills.\n\n
 ⚠ Lookalike: No dangerous lookalikes — only mushroom with downward-poi
 nting teeth under cap.\n\n💡 Harvest tip: Teeth rub off on fingers — g
 ood field ID. Mild nutty flavor.\n\n— Cedar · Northern California Forag
 ing App
CATEGORIES:MUSHROOMS,EASY
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
