  Aug\n\nHabitat: Intertidal rock pools\, exposed subtidal zone\nRegions: S
 onoma\, Mendocino\n\nHarvest tip: Harvest June–July at low tide only. Cu
 t blade leaving holdfast intact so it regrows annually. Do not rinse off w
 hite powdery surface — it's glutamates.\n\n— Cedar · Northern Califor
 nia Foraging App
CATEGORIES:COASTAL,PEAK
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
