 Harvest only young tightly-coiled shoots before unfolding. Wear gloves and
  long sleeves — sap causes blistering. Peel before eating. Cook thorough
 ly.\n\n— Cedar · Northern California Foraging App
CATEGORIES:GREENS,PEAK
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
